      "title": "Compare versions workflow notes",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "# Compare Two GenAsset Versions\n\n1. In GenAsset UI, open the same asset and click **Copy version id** for two versions.\n2. Paste older one in `left_version_id` and newer one in `right_version_id`.\n3. Queue the workflow.\n\nExpected result:\n- Left preview = left version image.\n- Right preview = right version image.\n- `diff_json` output contains prompt/model/seed/sampler/scheduler/steps/cfg/denoise differences.\n- `status_json` contains `ok: true`.\n\nIf it fails:\n- Check token and both version IDs belong to the same workspace.\n- Check both IDs are version ids (not asset id)."
      ],
      "color": "#243",
      "bgcolor": "#355"
    }
